{"tid":1965257,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"林鄭「搵食格」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-04-09T10:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T11:43:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f6cdf112053ac1919e23c1499292df174ac3cb4f","tid":1965257,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T10:55:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200409/20896534/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200409%2F20896534%2F&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVVTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=aec6d53f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200409%2F20896534%2F&h=16b6238c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200409/20896534/</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭「搵食格」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200409/large/1586336475_0521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200409%2Flarge%2F1586336475_0521.jpg&h=f0c244dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如今港人的活動範圍是居所與超市商場的雙向路，偶爾走過繁華區，已屬一場春夢，名店封以圍板，「奢侈品」無人問津，經常光顧的小店尤其食肆多已執笠，實在捱不住，加上「限聚令」雪上加霜，失業者眾，正是滿目瘡痍，屍橫遍野。<br />\n<br />\n正當武肺肆虐全球大流行之際，多國領袖苦民所苦，決定暫不支薪、減薪、捐薪、募款，援助財困基層：新加坡、馬來西亞、南韓、印度、菲律賓、肯雅、土耳其、烏克蘭、希臘&hellip;&hellip;的元首及內閣成員都在身體力行──全球只有林鄭毒娥及其庸劣班子，仍厚顏無恥地加薪。送中修例禍民害命、防疫遲鈍拙劣、死不封關、狗官尸位素餐、經濟重創&hellip;&hellip;還有資格年薪五百多萬外加酬酢津貼百萬？公帑白養一群廢柴，民憤民怨日深，定要合力迫減。<br />\n<br />\n毒娥死撐並非乘疫情嚴峻時加人工，而是去年7月時已調整計算──去年7月正是一百萬二百萬人上街反送中後，她仍口硬不肯「撤回」，引致後來黑警濫暴濫捕死傷無數的血腥鎮壓，還有臉？<br />\n<br />\n當然，林鄭六親緣薄又無朋友，明知自己時日無多，不狂撈些油水，報應來了，臨老唔過得世，長期醫療費難道靠年過三十仍口口聲聲「媽媽，媽媽」的裙腳仔？日後還得負擔4個龕位費用──難怪一副自私貪財「搵食格」，令人瞧不起。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"1101976e103f0b3a265984c600ff9b8493cf86f5","tid":1965257,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:16:09.000Z","msg":"咁直接嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ec3b5428ae226efd13c9b9b00fa1d65a0805b2","tid":1965257,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1101976e103f0b3a265984c600ff9b8493cf86f5","tid":1965257,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:16:09.000Z","msg":"咁直接嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"李碧華唔係不嬲都算直接架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c341a31b481cc6fe1b54961b60f296cd48dde07e","tid":1965257,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:25:41.000Z","msg":"林鄭六親緣薄又無朋友，明知自己時日無多，不狂撈些油水，報應來了，臨老唔過得世"},{"pid":"0cf23b90ca88f27234bf1a83e4941dc69ff73376","tid":1965257,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:30:59.000Z","msg":"好想知林博士係點睇佢老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe3916f0a46b1e5d4476f4a4cd4fc48860b756b","tid":1965257,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:43:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁直接嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n李碧華唔係不嬲都算直接架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到尾咪又係同肥狗黎細良太后之流，唔敢大屌幕後真魔鬼！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"}]}